          address, phone number, and credit card information. This personally identifiable information is used to acknowledge
          receipt of your donation for tax purposes and to include you on the Foundation's mailing list if you choose to
          join it. When you send a donation in honor or in memory of someone and request that an acknowledgement be sent
          to another individual or a family, we will use the name and address of that individual or family for acknowledgement
          purposes only.
        </p>
        <b>Security </b>
        <p>
